data.description: Welcome to Fairfield Harbour! This updated home is ready for new owners! As you enter the home you are greeted by an entryway overlooking the formal dining room and living space. The kitchen features plenty of counter space, stainless steel appliances, along with a separate eat in area. The owners suite offers a walk in closet along with an en-suite bathroom. The other 2 bedrooms are located just down the hall and have a full bathroom to share. Stepping outside, enjoy the screened in patio out back. The home has a new crawlspace with a transferrable warranty. This home is a must see...schedule your showing today!
